{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2e696696e","title":"在山东省军区关于山东地区把斗争锋芒指向解放军的报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b36471605c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":7,"articleId":"f2e696696e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"6e8c255b63","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军山东省军区1967年5月4日给济南军区并中共中央文革小组、全军文革小组的电报。电报说，山东地区目前的斗争锋芒指向了解放军，越来越明显，已波及各地区。主要表现是：一、到处张贴、散发攻击解放军的大字报、标语、传单，省军区、军分区和县市武装部参加“三结合”的领导干部，几乎都被公开点名，成为打倒的主要对象。二、冲击军事机关，围攻、绑架部队人员。三、悔、段打和斗争解放军干部、战士。以上情况正在向基层发展，使许多军分区、县市武装部无法进行工作，严重影响了战备等工作的进行。客地“三结合”的临时权力机构已有不少处于换状态。这种事态如果继续发展下去，将会使工农业生产受到严重影响。"},{"id":"faa546d29c","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"“八·一五”是当时重庆大学的一个群众造反组织。"},{"id":"1d758b4564","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"梁，指梁兴初，张，指张国华，廿，指甘渭汉，韦，指韦杰，当时分别担任中国人民解放军成都军区司令员、第一政委、第四政委和副司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bf009c883e","type":"title","text":"在山东省军区关于山东地区把斗争锋芒指向解放军的报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e8c255b63","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来”、文革小组各同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"faa546d29c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件回请阅。看来山东学生、工人出事地点（就全省说，占少数），省军区、军分区、县人武部，大都可能有些问题。此事应如何解决，请你们研究出办法，告我为盼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d758b4564","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4cc8d865b8","type":"paragraph","text":"五月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b74b3ab18","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]林彪，当时任中共中央军委副主席，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。恩来，即周恩来。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7229e02756","type":"paragraph","text":"山东及各省，正规军弄错的较少。重庆54军有电报说关于支持重大八·一五”是否错误问题，宜找两方面人都来，和梁、张、甘、书请同志共同商处。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a6484cb3f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东又及","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":458,"end":457}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1419b1e671","type":"title","text":"在山东省军区关于山东地区把斗争锋芒指向解放军的报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c6dd8dba8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"208abc087c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请阅。看来山东学生、工人出事地点（就全省说，占少数），省军区、军分区、县人武部，大都可能有些问题。此事应如何解决，请你们研究出办法，告我为盼！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c0849f750","type":"paragraph","text":"在山东省军区关于山东地区把斗争锋芒指向解放军的报告上的批语","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d217c18c0","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来、文革小组各同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ef077e0a5","type":"paragraph","text":"山东及各省，正规军弄错的较少。重庆54军有电报说关于支持重大八·一五是否错误问题，宜找两方面人都来，和梁、张、甘、韦诸同志共同商处。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b804c7dda7","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.05.07","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f2e696696e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}